* {{tl|Nihongo3}}, essentially the same as {{tl|Nihongo}}, but gives romaji first and English inside the parentheses
* {{tl|Nihongo krt}}, essentially the same as {{tl|Nihongo}}, but gives kanji first with rōmaji and English inside the parentheses
* {{tl|Nihongo2}}, also displays the kanji properly, but without adding anything in parentheses, without romaji and without the extra parameters
